    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "=Quick question for {{ $json.firstName }} at {{ $json.enriched_companyName }}",
        "message": "=<html>\n<body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;\">\n\n<p>Hi {{ $json.firstName }},</p>\n\n<p>I came across <strong>{{ $json.enriched_companyName }}</strong> and wanted to reach out personally — I think there's a strong fit here.</p>\n\n<p>I'm Promise, COO at <strong>DropMeds</strong>. We help {{ $json.enriched_industry }} companies automate their lead pipelines and sales outreach — so your team only ever speaks to qualified, ready-to-buy prospects.</p>\n\n<p>Here's what that looks like in practice:</p>\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 20px;\">\n  <li>Leads verified and scored automatically within seconds</li>\n  <li>Personalised emails sent before your competitor even sees the lead</li>\n  <li>CRM updated in real time — zero manual data entry</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Would you be open to a quick 30-minute call this week? No sales pitch — just a honest conversation about whether this makes sense for {{ $json.enriched_companyName }}.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 28px 0;\">\n  <a href=\"https://your_calendy_link/min\"\n     style=\"background:#0066cc; color:white; padding:12px 24px; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold;\">\n    Book a Free 30-min Call\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p>Best,<br/>\n<strong>your-name</strong><br/>\nCOO &middot; DropMeds<br/>\n+234 912663</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee; margin-top:32px;\"/>\n<p style=\"font-size:11px; color:#999;\">You're receiving this because your contact details were shared with us. Reply STOP to unsubscribe at any time.</p>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
        "options": {}
      },
