    {
      "parameters": {
        "sendTo": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "=Still thinking it over, {{ $json.firstName }}?",
        "message": "=<html>\n<body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;\">\n\n<p>Hi {{ $json.firstName }},</p>\n\n<p>I reached out a few days ago — just wanted to follow up in case it got buried.</p>\n\n<p>Here's a result from a recent client in the {{ $json.enriched_industry }} space:</p>\n\n<blockquote style=\"border-left: 4px solid #0066cc; margin: 20px 0; padding: 12px 20px; background: #f4f8ff; border-radius: 4px; color: #444;\">\n\"We cut our manual lead handling time from 4 hours a day to zero. The pipeline just runs itself.\"\n<br/><em>— Operations Lead, B2B SaaS</em>\n</blockquote>\n\n<p>If the timing isn't right, no problem at all — just reply and I'll check back in a month.</p>\n\n<p>But if you're even a little curious, let's get 30 minutes on the calendar:</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 28px 0;\">\n  <a href=\"https://calendly.com/sundaepromix/30min\"\n     style=\"background:#0066cc; color:white; padding:12px 24px; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold;\">\n    Grab 30 Mins With Promise\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<p>Hope things are going well at {{ $json.enriched_companyName }}.</p>\n\n<p>Best,<br/>\n<strong>Promise</strong><br/>\nCOO &middot; DropMeds<br/>\n+234 912663</p>\n\n<hr style=\"border:none; border-top:1px solid #eee; margin-top:32px;\"/>\n<p style=\"font-size:11px; color:#999;\">Reply STOP to unsubscribe.</p>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
        "options": {}
      },
